The paper discusses the challenges and opportunities of distributed machine learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) that involves the use of distributed systems (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS) to improve the efficiency and scalability of machine learning algorithms. The paper also discusses the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY) in distributed machine learning.
